station_location.access_point: The station's entrance and lounge will extend from the terminal, while the station platform will align with the terminal's third level.
Bayview station is located near the eastern edge of Hintonburg, off Albert and Scott streets.
Bowesville Station is situated east of Bowesville Road and south of Earl Armstrong Road.
The station is located at the intersection of Campus Avenue and Library Road. With entrances on both the east and west sides, the current fare-paid zone entrances will be maintained.
Greenboro Station is situated on Bank Street, west of the Transitway Station.
Leitrim Station is located south of Leitrim Road

Positioned west of Limebank Road, south of Earl Armstrong Road, and east of Main Street, it has a single entrance where fares are paid. This entrance provides access to Main Street, the northeast-west Connector Road, and the future southeast-west Connector Road.
Mooney's Bay Station is south of Heron Road
South Keys Station is located next to the South Keys Shopping Centre
Uplands Station is conveniently located right next to the EY Centre, with a direct sidewalk connection to the centre.
Walkley Station is east of the Southeast Transitway Station on Walkley Road
the station is found just north of Carling Avenue. It is conveniently connected to an adjacent multi-use pathway (MUP) on the east.
